packets.name: Voxiletten
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: The perfect companion for sports and relaxation. Or when you quickly need shoes to greet the pizza delivery guy while you are having a lazy afternoon on the couch. They are not only lightweight and super endurable, they are also sustainable as they are made of recycled voxels! Designer: Lorex for PIXL | pixls.eth (ethical blockchain fashion from Austria). Manufactured with MagicaVoxel.
